  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nMetrics defined [here](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/unstable/packages/validator/src/metrics.ts) are not showing up in the metrics endpoints and consequently not showing up in grafana.\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl localhost:8008/metrics | grep vc_\r\n  % Total    % Received % Xferd  Average Speed   Time    Time     Time  Current\r\n                                 Dload  Upload   Total   Spent    Left  Speed\r\n100 79199    0 79199    0     0  3132k      0 --:--:-- --:--:-- --:--:-- 4070k\r\n```\r\n\r\nAre these metrics work in progress? If so then this issue should be about wrapping that up and getting the metrics to be collected. If it is a bug, then this issue should be about fixing it and getting the metrics collected.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nThe `vc_` metrics should be exposing metrics data at a known endpoint and should be collected and displayed in grafana.\r\n",
